Begin fools_dead_check

;flag for dialog to recognize that troublesome fools bothering Huleeya have been killed, quest A1-7 Huleeya Informant

short FoolsDead

if ( MenuMode == 1 )
	Return
endif

if ( GetDeadCount, "Favel Gobor" > 0 )
	if ( GetDeadCount, "Urven Davor" > 0)
		if ( GetDeadCount, "Ethys Savil" > 0)
			set FoolsDead to 1
		endif
	endif
endif

End
